Description_lang: Increases the damage of Devouring Plague by $s3% and causes it to deal its damage over $s1 sec, but increases its Insanity cost by ${$s5/100}.

description_blz.en_US: Increases the damage of Devouring Plague by 20% and causes it to deal its damage over 12 sec, but increases its Insanity cost by 5.
description_blz.es_MX: Aumenta un 20% el daño de Peste devoradora, con lo que inflige su daño durante 12 s, pero aumenta su costo de demencia en 5.
description_blz.pt_BR: Aumenta em 20% o dano de Peste Devoradora e a faz causar todo o dano ao longo de 12 s, mas o custo de Insanidade aumenta em 5.
description_blz.de_DE: Erhöht den Schaden von 'Verschlingende Seuche' um 20% und verursacht den Schaden stattdessen im Verlauf von 12 Sek., erhöht allerdings die Wahnsinnskosten um 5.
description_blz.en_GB: Increases the damage of Devouring Plague by 20% and causes it to deal its damage over 12 sec, but increases its Insanity cost by 5.
description_blz.es_ES: Aumenta un 20% el daño de Peste devoradora y provoca que inflija su daño a lo largo de 12 s, pero su coste de demencia aumenta 5 p.
description_blz.fr_FR: Les dégâts de Peste dévorante sont augmentés de 20% et ce sort inflige ses dégâts en 12 s, mais son coût en insanité est augmenté de 5.
description_blz.it_IT: Aumenta i danni inflitti da Piaga Divoratrice del 20% e fa sì che infligga i danni in 12 s, ma ne aumenta il costo in pazzia di 5.
description_blz.ru_RU: Увеличивает урон "Всепожирающей чумы" на 20%. Теперь она наносит урон в течение 12 сек. и тратит на 5 больше безумия.
description_blz.ko_KR: 파멸의 역병의 공격력이 20%만큼 증가하고 12초에 걸쳐 피해를 입히도록 합니다. 하지만 광기 소모량이 5만큼 증가합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 噬靈瘟疫的傷害提高20%，並變成在12秒內造成傷害，但消耗的瘋狂提高5點。
description_blz.zh_CN: 噬灵疫病的伤害提高20%，并使其在12秒内造成伤害，但消耗的狂乱值提高5点。
